# Intentionally empty for v1.
#
# This CLI does not call any LLM directly. The LLM work happens inside
# Claude-in-Cowork, via the skills under /skills/. The user's Cowork
# subscription supplies the LLM; the CLI does pure template-fill.
#
# If you ever add a standalone (non-Cowork) LLM path, this is where the
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY would go. Until then, leave this file alone.
